-- Tronox CEO Has ‘Reasons to Think About’ Buying Rockwood Assets
-- B y   J a c k   K a s k e y
-- 2013-02-21T15:01:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-21/tronox-ceo-has-reasons-to-think-about-buying-rockwood-assets.html
Tronox Ltd. (TROX)  Chairman and Chief
Executive Officer Tom Casey said the U.S. maker of titanium-
dioxide pigments “has reasons to think about” buying assets
from  Rockwood Holdings Inc. (ROC)   Casey commented today on his company’s earnings conference
call.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jack Kaskey in Houston at 
